  "Paywall.nwFAQ.question_1": "What is Mimika?",
  "Paywall.nwFAQ.answer_1": "Mimika is a mobile app which was created so that those suffering from weak jawline or unsatisfactory facial aesthetics could train and improve their jaw, facial muscles and overall appearance.The app contains many features: personalized mewing training program, video guidance, progress evaluation tracker, daily reminders, face toning workouts, educational content.{br}{br}Each training plan is created by our team of dentistry and facial surgery specialists who tailor the activities and advice depending on your personal needs.{br}{br}And you can reach all of it on your mobile phone – through the Mimika app – available on both iOS and Android.",
  "Paywall.nwFAQ.question_2": "How is my plan prepared?",
  "Paywall.nwFAQ.answer_2": "Our team of dentistry and facial surgery specialists evaluates the answers you provide in the quiz and creates your personalized plan based on it. Each program is crafted individually, so you get access to a custom plan that really works for your particular situation.",
  "Paywall.nwFAQ.question_3": "What happens after I order?",
  "Paywall.nwFAQ.answer_3": "Your personalized workout plan is created using the answers you provided in the quiz. After completing the order – you will have full access to your plan and video guidance that comes with it.{br}{br}You will receive an email with instructions on how to activate your account in 3 easy steps:{br}1. Create your account to get to your personal workout plan.{br}2. Download Mimika app to your mobile phone from the App Store or Google Play Store – depending on if you use an iPhone or Android phone.{br}3. Login to Mimika app and start your transformation!",
  "Paywall.nwFAQ.question_4": "How can I cancel my subscription?",
  "Paywall.nwFAQ.answer_4": "If you decide to cancel your subscription, you can do so by contacting us via email {email}.",
  "Paywall.nwFAQ.answer_4.email": "support@mimika-app.com",
  "Paywall.ourPromise.Title": "Our Promise",
  "Paywall.ourPromise.Text": "Proper mewing technique, when used continuously, gets to the bottom of almost every problem that affects your facial features: weak jawline, misaligned teeth, asymmetrical or chubby face, double chin, turtle neck, bad posture, nasal congestion, mouth breathing.{br}{br}Created and verified by orthodontist Dr. Derrick Sherman",
