  "Stripe.AutoRenew.Paywall.FallOffer": "This Special Offer includes a free {trialPeriodValue}-{trialPeriodUnit} trial of Mimika Academy. Auto-renews at {billingPeriod}/{billingPeriodUnit} unless cancelled.",
  "Onboarding.Paywall.Main.Question.Bullet3.Bundle.Text": "You’ll get your personal plan shortly with bonus access to Mimika Academy to guide you further.",
  "Onboarding.Paywall.Main.Bullet6.Bundle": "Expert insights from Academy",
  "Onboarding.MwVisibleChanges.Slide1": "I was skeptical at first, but wow—my profile has changed! The exercises are simple but so effective. Sticking to this plan was the best decision I made for my face.",
  "Onboarding.MwVisibleChanges.Slide2": "This program turned mewing from something I struggled with into an automatic habit. My face feels stronger, and my breathing has improved too. Crazy how something so small can make such a big difference!",
  "Onboarding.MwVisibleChanges.Slide3": "I’ve always struggled with my facial posture, but this program made everything so clear! After just a few weeks, I already feel a huge difference. My jawline looks more defined, and mewing finally became second nature. Highly recommend!",
