  "Paywall.Premium.Assistant.GetGuidance": "Get real-time guidance on jawline training, tongue posture & facial symmetry",
  "Paywall.Premium.Assistant.Features.feature1": "Personalized feedback on your mewing technique",
  "Paywall.Premium.Assistant.Features.feature2": "Science-based analysis of your jaw and posture",
  "Paywall.Premium.Assistant.Features.feature3": "Daily micro-corrections for real progress",
  "Paywall.Premium.Assistant.Features.feature4": "Track your face transformation over time",
  "Paywall.Premium.Assistant.Declaimer": "Mimika will use your payment details to seamlessly process future payments. All transactions will be converted into USD based on your bank’s exchange rate at the time of payment. This is a one-time  payment offer with lifetime access. {strong} If you cannot get the access, please email our support team at {supportLink}. You may also want to take a screenshot of this information for your reference.",
  "Paywall.Premium.Assistant.Declaimer.Strong": "This purchase cannot be refunded.",
  "Paywall.AcademyImprove.SpecialDeal.Text": "Not sure where to start? Your personal assistant will guide you — skincare, metabolism, confidence included.",
  "Onboarding.mwWomenVisibleChanges.Slide1.Text": "Yesterday my daughter told me she has a beautiful mom, I almost cried because I can't remember the last time I had time for myself. Thanks to Mimika, I was able to regain my sense of self!",
  "Onboarding.mwWomenVisibleChanges.Slide2.Text": "I started gaining weight after surgery and then abruptly lost it and my face started drooping, I was horrified. After 3 weeks of my routine, I noticed my face shape recovered, swelling went away and (thank goodness) my second chin started to go away!",
  "Onboarding.mwWomenVisibleChanges.Slide3.Text": "I quit skincare due to allergies, wasted money, and products, that just don't work. My mom recommended Mimika for its natural approach. Now, it's my go-to pocket beautician for every occasion. The program helped me with was swelling after a party, no patches would have done the trick!",
  "Onboarding.Mewing.Man.Loader.Card1.Main": "I started just out of curiosity, but after a few weeks I could clearly see the difference. My jawline looks sharper, and I finally like my profile photos. The exercises are simple, but they really work. Highly recommended.",
  "Onboarding.Mewing.Man.Loader.Card2.Main": "I didn’t expect mewing to have such an impact. My face looks more defined and less tired. I feel more confident in real life and on camera now.",
  "Onboarding.Mewing.Man.Loader.Card2.Title": "Better face, better confidence",
  "Onboarding.Mewing.Man.Loader.Card3.Title": "Real results without surgery",
  "Onboarding.Mewing.Man.Loader.Card3.Main": "I always had a bit of a double chin even though I’m not overweight. After a month, my neck and jaw look noticeably slimmer. No pain, no surgery — just results.",
  "Onboarding.Mewing.Women.Loader.Card2.Title": "My face looks lifted...",
  "Onboarding.Mewing.Women.Loader.Card2.Main": "I started noticing changes after just 2–3 weeks. My face looks tighter, my cheekbones are more defined, and even my makeup looks better on my skin. I love the results.",
  "Onboarding.Mewing.Women.Loader.Card3.Title": "Goodbye, nasolabial folds",
  "Onboarding.Mewing.Women.Loader.Card3.Main": "I was already thinking about cosmetic procedures because of my smile lines. But this app actually helped — my face looks fresher and more youthful now.",
  "Onboarding.Mewing.Women.Loader.Card4.Title": "Natural beauty without injections",
  "Onboarding.Mewing.Women.Loader.Card4.Main": "I wanted a natural way to improve my face without fillers or injections. This app was exactly what I needed. My face shape looks more refined and balanced now.",
  "Onboarding.mwBiteType.Title": "What is your bite type?",
  "Onboarding.Mewing.ImproveLife.Disclaimer": "Data from a scientific study carried out by UCLA Department of Medicine",
